2010-06-25  Michael Meissner  <meissner@linux.vnet.ibm.com>

	* config/rs6000/rs6000-protos.h
	(rs6000_expand_convert_si_to_sfdf): Add declaration.

	* config/rs6000/rs6000.opt (-mfcfid): New switch.

