	(UNSPEC_LFIWZX): Ditto.
	(SFDF): New iterator.
	(rreg2): New mode attribute.
	(SIGN_SI_CVT_FP): Ditto.
	(UNS_SI_CVT_FP): Ditto.
	(rsqrt<mode>2): Use RS6000_RECIP_HAVE_RSQRTE_P.
